name: Boss Nass (AI)
Lore: 'Ankura Gungan who is the leader of his people. Prone to nervous tics. Personally responsible for uniting the Ankura and Otolla races together.',
Text: 'While at an underwater site and all of your characters on Naboo are Gungans: add one battle destiny in battles at Naboo sites and once during your deploy phase may deploy a Gungan or Steady, Steady from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
